{"id":335214,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/南方都市报-昆明火车站乘客遭袭记录/","date":"2014-03-02T05:50:23Z","modified":"2014-03-02T19:34:19Z","title":"南方都市报 | 昆明火车站乘客遭袭记录","content":"<p>@南方都市报 ：【昆明火车站乘客遭袭记录】值班民警称，行凶者从火车站的铜牛雕像处开始砍杀路人。目击者描述，行凶者有几个共同点：手持长刀，身穿黑衣。其中两个黑衣人从1号售票窗口往7号售票窗口袭击，砍人的同时说着人们听不懂的话。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6204ece1gw1ee18l9nqkpj20c82be7k0.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-335215\" alt=\"6204ece1gw1ee18l9nqkpj20c82be7k0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6204ece1gw1ee18l9nqkpj20c82be7k0.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"3002\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6204ece1gw1ee18l9nqkpj20c82be7k0.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/6204ece1gw1ee18l9nqkpj20c82be7k0-150x1024.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,20505],"tags":[20427,17837,24714,21293,9503,24051]}